Author: kahnchat
Title: ⭐[ANN][ICO]⭐⭐⭐⭐KahnChat Mobile Payment and Social Networking Crowdsale Live Now
Body: Does the figure “8.95 m (29 ft 4 1⁄4 in)” bring any flashback memories to you?. Well if you are one of those Snapchats and Instagram sedated millennial then maybe you don’t know much about this. But a google search and you would know why I mention this in this blog. 8.95 stands as a true testimony to individual human effort and endurance. At the summer Olympics 1991, Mike Powell with his inhuman leap broke the world record for long jump beating the previous record of 8.90 meters by Bob Beamon at the 1968 Mexico City Olympics. However, the fun fact is this my friend: “The record is still unbroken till date”.  KahnChat’s vision to implement XMPP protocol on BlockChain based networks is one such leap that requires human intelligence and effort to a scale equivalent achieving an Olympic feat that lasts decades. However, we at KahnChat believe this is just a milestone in our long journey ahead. On the hindsight, KahnChat hopes to create a service that empowers its user community with the power sprint to make the great leap into the yet partly unknown but better and secure world of cryptocurrencies and blockchain.  As per reports, DARPA (US Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency) called for a proposal of a secure messaging and transaction platform based on the decentralized network to facilitate individuals to send secure messages or conduct fair transactions recorded on a decentralized ledger as proof of work.  The above objective of the DARPA’s proposal further cements KahnChats vision of the future. In this blog, we try to understand the ins and outs of the IM Protocol or the XMPP architecture. We also throw light on some of the possible solution paths we are working on to migrate XMPP features on BlockChain.  Why XMPP?  XMPP enables bi-directional content sharing between individuals or groups on the TCP/IP protocol. Some important features that KahnChat thrives each day to emulate on its BlockChain based Wallet cum Social Media App are:  One-to-One as well as Multi-Party Messaging  Contact Inventory: Access to User approved Contacts  Subscriptions Details and User Notifications  The above features make XMPP a goto feature for chat apps. Developers use these to make secure and easily scalable apps for app stores. Hence, a similar feature in blockchain will open the Pandora’s box for scalability.  Slow Blocks are the RoadBlocks  Scalability is a major roadblock for blockchain based systems or services. To scale a system that copies all the transaction it undertakes is a humongous task involving a lot of time, space and an extremely efficient resource management.  Ethereum is one of the many different blockchains. Let us look at some of its technical parameters.  No of Transactions Confirmed per Second on the Ethereum Blockchain  15 tx/s  Confirmation time in the Ethereum network  14.8 seconds(on 19 Feb, 2018 )  In the last year or so, the demand for Ethereum network has increased manifold. This is mainly facilitated by the increasing number of ICO’s using Ethereum network. Hence the network is congested and loaded.  Possible Solution  The Future Highway  The blockchain is still a very raw technology with great untapped potential. Ethereum has deployed Raiden Network to resolve the scalability issue. This would be followed by the Metropolis and Serenity (Beta Solutions). Solution deployment will drain time, money and most important of them all: quality network architects. Plasma networks though in its infancy are supposed to increase tx/s to “billions per second”.  Now, where does KahnChat app fit on all this?  IM features like instant responses, instant updates etc cannot be implemented on the present blockchain technology. The herculean task demands technical expertise as well as a financial backup. Hence, with the enough ICO fund, we would like to conduct a thorough research on it and accomplish following goals in the upcoming months:  The KahnChat ICO fund will be primarily used to unlock this black box of the BlockChain network. The roadmap for our solution to Scalability of Ethereum Blocks and in the process implement IM features on our app will involve:  Low Latency blocks: Using a P2P network based on the internet to determine an alternative ledger (by ledger we mean transactions, texts, videos, purchase orders etc).  Decentralise IM nodes: Homomorphic encryption could be a possible viable solution. The Consensus building blocks are allowed to act on the incoming data. The nodes, however, do not have any access to the information content of Data. The encrypted solution for data. The developers can also use encrypted public keys to conceal all transactions sent between desired recipient and the consensus building system.  The Third Phase of KahnChat’s KCH ICO is live now. Thrilled and excited by the great public response to the second phase, KahnChat is now offering great Special Bonus Scheme to its early token buyers. Please visit the website http://www.kahnchat.com to know more about the sales schedule and bonus details. We at Team kahnChat are sure that with the raised Fund Money , we would be able to find the scalability solution and implement IM services on Blockchain network.

Title: ⭐[ANN][ICO]⭐⭐⭐⭐KahnChat Mobile Payment and Social Networking Crowdsale Live Now
Body: Well, it isn't too expensive to develop the exchange platform. Difficulty? The answer is Yes and No. There is nothing is easy but there is nothing is impossible in the world of programming. This is achievable.  To explain how the exchange work in a none too technical terms, you can think it in this way for the current exchange. 1) The website is the User interface to communicate with the server to retrieve information and display it on screen. KahnChat app is serve the same purpose, it is an user interface to talk to the server, send a request to the server and get the response back to display on the screen. 2) The server installed the different blockchain algorithm and talk to the blockchain network. Receive request from the interface, communicate with the blockchain network and return the result back from the blockchain network then pass it back to the user interface.  The above is not a technical way to explain the entire workflow but more in common language that everyone can understand.

Body: The mobile payment target is 1% of the market share in 3 years. As the app has integrated social networking, the user base will grow faster than any mobile payment app who without the social networking features.  According to "The Statistics Portal" source, the total value of card transactions in the United Kingdom, Germany, France, Italy and Netherlands for the year 2016 is 1787.8b €. A 1% market share (assuming the card transaction spent does not increase for the next three years), the potential yearly mobile payment transaction turn over for KahnChat mobile payment is 17.8b €.  The KahnChat transaction fee is set to only 0.6% per transaction from merchant, this gives a potential of 107m € yearly revenue to KahnChat.  The above forecast is only from 5 EU states, there are still another 22 EU states and other countries mobile payment transaction is not yet in the calculation.  The Cryptocurrency transaction is also another income stream to KahnChat. As KahnChat support BTC, ETH, LTC, DASH, BCH and KCH, in fact, KahnChat is also a mini exchange by itself, it allows the user to buy and sell their cryptocurrency where KahnChat supported. The exchange fees will become another income stream to KahnChat.  By year 3, the KahnChat Gaming Platform should be implemented, where the user can play online games, buy upgrade package or game credit. This form another income stream to KahnChat.

Author: kahnchat
Title: ⭐[ANN][ICO]⭐⭐⭐⭐KahnChat Mobile Payment and Social Networking Crowdsale Live Now
Body: For mobile payment, the app divided into a different section. Fiat or Cryptocurrency. To completely have the app run in blockchain, it takes times to develop the smart contract, test it and even might need to develop our own blockchain if necessary. So the beginning stage of the project is to get the function and features running first even some of the features are still implementing the current standard technology.  1) Fiat Currency: At the beginning, the Fiat currency is still using the standard technology, implementing the industry security as to what other financial institution applied to ensure the security of the user's fund. The blockchain technology for fiat currency will in research and development during this stage, it will take many steps, procedures, testing, fixing before it can be officially launched to the public. User's fund security is our priority.  Fund transfer for Fiat currency at this stage is not in blockchain technology but standard well-known technology. Fund uses for purchase are taking off from the user's account balance with multiple security measurements including 2 factors confirmation with fingerprint, security code or message code etc.  2) Cryptocurrency The merchant who wishes to accept cryptocurrency as a payment source instead of Fiat currency is the cryptocurrency user too. The Merchant also need to agree to the terms of use and make themselves aware of the possible network congestion might cause the payment in cryptocurrency would not be able to give instant confirmation. We are not the one who makes cryptocurrency wallet and payment, the blockchain technology uses on the cryptocurrency wallet and payment is not a new technology but consider semi-mutual technology. The Merchant will need to wait for the confirmation before releasing the goods.

Body: The app is in the development, estimate beta version release for the social networking features is scheduled on the Q2 2018.  We charge 0.6% transaction fees to the merchant for mobile payment for goods and service purchase not for exchange fiat currency <=> cryptocurrency.  The app will have an internal exchange centre to allows users selling and buying cryptocurrency from and to other users.  Selling Cryptocurrency: - User A put a sell on the KahnChat internal exchange. - User B buy it - Fund taking off from User B account balance (fiat currency) - Fund transfer to User A account balance (fiat currency) - Cryptocurrency transfer to User B cryptocurrency wallet  The objective of KahnChat project is to deliver an All-One app where it can support i) Mobile payment features in Fiat currency with or without limits set (user preferences setting) ii) Mobile payment features in Cryptocurrency allows merchant who wishes to accept cryptocurrency as a mode of payment. iii) Cryptocurrency <=> Fiat Exchanging in one place iv) Fund transfer to other users without knowing their bank details v) Integrated Social Networking allows the user to connect to other users without the need of download another app vi) Pages follow in one place vii) Post sharing in one place viii) Issue discount code and send to followers in one place (Merchant service features)  There are lots more features can be added during the development but all these not going to happen overnight. It will be implemented step by step,  No business can be run without compliance with the regulations. The features where KahnChat aims to implement is not a new feature in the globe but a combination of the best features into One.  We are definitely following the country laws and regulations for each feature.

Author: kahnchat
Title: ⭐[ANN][ICO]⭐⭐⭐⭐KahnChat Mobile Payment and Social Networking Crowdsale Live Now
Body: KahnChat is not a traditional mobile payment. The current model of the mobile payment is a virtual card storage, its turn the user physical card into a virtual card and link it with a Direct Debit agreement to allows the processor to take fund directly from the user bank account.  KahnChat mobile payment is operating in a different process. 1) The user adds fund to KahnChat account via a Direct Debit agreement. 2) The user spent from the KahnChat account balance not directly from their Cards or Bank account. 3) The user initial fund transfer from the KahnChat account balance to another KahnChat user's account, the process is not directly from the user's Cards or Bank account. 4) The user withdraws fund from KahnChat account balance to the bank account registered on file. 5) KahnChat initial SWIFT or SEPA fund transfer to the user's cards or bank account.  KahnChat is an All-One app, our objective is to turn KahnChat app to become one of the useful app for the user, the numbers of messages send/receive is more than the numbers of the transaction. So we choose to use 'Chat' instead of wallet, payment, crypto, network, app etc.

KahnChat is a mobile payment feature where merchant do not need a card reader (small merchant) but just their mobile phone. There is no cost involved for them like the traditional card machine. For the large orgainisation, we have the plan to offer them the solution to accept our mobile payment without the need to replace their current POS system.  Is it difficult to get merchant onboard? The answer is "Yes" and "No" "Yes" if the app has no users base, but we have a large number of users who interested in our app features and project idea. You can check out our Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/kahntechltd/ for the number of users likes our posts, videos, and the page about the project idea.  "No" If there is users base and offer low transaction fees to the merchant. No merchant wish to pay a high transaction fee for accepting card payment, the lowest fee they can get the more profits for their business. Traditional payment processor or card machine charge 1.5% to 5% per transaction fees. KahnChat payment system plan to charge only 0.6% per transaction fees.   How we get the user to start using our app when we launch it? This is why we need to raise fund through Initial Coin Offering. There are plenty of solutions to increase user base, the only matter is the financial support. We set 50% of our raised fund for our marketing and promotional budget. The world gameplay was changed, the success not only because of a good idea or a good app but a strong financial support and user base is the key to a successful business. With the fund raised, we can have more engineers, contractors, partners to make the app features faster. Development cost monies in wages but not as huge as the marketing expenses. With the support of the users, buyers and investors, we can have the app launch as per our schedule.   Is mobile payment the only income stream for the business? Mobile payment is one of the income streams for KahnChat app. According to 'The UK Cards Association' source, the UK alone had £643.6b cards amount spent in the year 2016.  KahnChat mobile payment target is 1% of the market share after mobile payment app launch, this comes to £64b transaction amounts per year.  KahnChat mobile payment transaction fee for the merchant is only 0.6% per transaction. This gives the company a potential of £3.84m income stream alone from the mobile payment feature.  The forecast above yet to include the other 27 EU member states and other countries. The potential growth of the company is very positive.  KahnChat digital wallet accepts not only the fiat currency but also the cryptocurrency, this allows the user to cash in their cryptocurrency into KahnChat wallet for purchase or withdraw.
